1. **Migrate DB**: `python -m app.repositories.migrate` (Step 2).
2. **Run FastAPI**: `uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8080` (Step 9 + this step).
3. **Register Webhook** (replace placeholders):

curl -s "https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/setWebhook" \
-d url="https://<PUBLIC_HTTPS_URL>/tg/webhook" \
-d secret_token="<SECRET>"


# 1) Apply migrations locally or inside container
python -m app.repositories.migrate

# 2) Build & run
docker compose up --build -d

# 3) Set webhook
curl -s "https://api.telegram.org/bot$BOT_TOKEN/setWebhook" \
  -d url="https://<PUBLIC_HTTPS_URL>/tg/webhook" \
  -d secret_token="$TG_WEBHOOK_SECRET"